data.description: New Price! Country setting ideal for any outdoorsperson, sportsman, mechanic or nature lover! 3.3 acre wooded lot with outbuildings and trails in West Cocalico Twp. This property has been well maintained and offers wooded seclusion with easy access and plenty of space for whatever you need. Open lawn in the front, attached garage converted to useable interior space, detached garage for workshop, concrete patio between house and detached garage with doggy door entries, flat driveway and abundant parking, fenced in rear yard, fenced in kennel, gazebo, shed, wood shed, portable shed, woods trails, pond, pasturable land, and livestock animals permitted! Wildlife abounds. Featuring a living room with a view, enclosed 3 season sunroom with woodland views, 3 or 4 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, hardwood floors, combo kitchen/dining area, new expansive deck with wooded view, new siding, new paneling, new windows, finished lower level and a pretty setting in Cocalico School District. Great country property with open space and woods.  Do not miss this one! Schedule your showing today!
